      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/kim-jong-un-tests-new-rockets-to-strike-seoul-and-perhaps-sell-to-putin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[领导人金正恩监督了朝鲜新型火箭系统的测试，该系统可以增强他攻击首尔的能力，并且可能成为他试图出售给俄罗斯用于攻击乌克兰的武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/kim-jong-un-tests-new-rockets-to-strike-seoul-and-perhaps-sell-to-putin</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 01:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
